  "description": "A liberty in [weiqi](../_index.md) is an empty intersection directly adjacent to a stone or connected group of stones [@nagofed2026thisisgo]. Liberties determine whether a group remains on the board. When the last liberty is removed, the group is subject to [capture](./capture.md).",
